'''Antoine Wendo Kolosoy''' (abótámí o mokɔlɔ 25 apríli 1925; akúfí o mokɔlɔ 28 yúli 2008) azalí [[moyémbi]] mpé mokeli wa nzémbo wa [[Kongó-Kinsásá]].

== Diski ==
[[File:Ngoma1986 Trio bow 78.jpg|thumb|200px|right|The "''Trio Bow''" recording of "akeyi na zandu" (1956) on the [[Ngoma (record label)|Ngoma records]] label.  Wendo, [[Antoine Bukasa]] and [[Manuel D’Oliveira]], stars individually, were combined into this supergroup in 1955 by Nicolas Jéronimidis.]] 
